WEBVTT

00:00:00.216 --> 00:00:01.704
Sometimes a diseased

00:00:01.700 --> 00:00:03.016
or damaged knee joint

00:00:03.010 --> 00:00:05.416
is replaced with an artificial joint.

00:00:05.560 --> 00:00:07.288
Most replacement knee joints

00:00:07.280 --> 00:00:08.784
include a metal femoral

00:00:08.780 --> 00:00:10.400
or thighbone component

00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:12.448
and a plastic and metal tibial

00:00:12.440 --> 00:00:14.280
or shinbone component.

00:00:14.512 --> 00:00:16.408
The damaged portion of the kneecap

00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:17.480
or patella

00:00:17.480 --> 00:00:18.824
may be replaced by a

00:00:18.820 --> 00:00:20.840
mushroom shaped prosthesis.

00:00:21.168 --> 00:00:22.888
The resectioned patella

00:00:22.880 --> 00:00:24.032
and prosthesis

00:00:24.030 --> 00:00:26.720
are attached to the other components.

